e: ￹`O~ `tatiih~`ay~ `a~ `tamdaw~ `cingra~.￺He is an evil person.￻他是邪惡的人
￹`Tatiih~ `ko~ `ngoyos~ `nira~.￺He spreads gossip.￻他是善於撒播謠言的人
￹`Tatiih'~ `ko~ `harateng~ `ako~.￺I don't feel good about (something).￻我很不高興，我對(那些事情)感覺欠佳
￹`Yo~ `paka~`tengil~ `kako~ `i~ `sa~`tatiih~ `sa~`~ `ko~ `harateng~ `ako~.￺When I heard that, my attitude changed.￻當我聽到(那些消息)後，心裡很難過
￹`Aka~ `pi~`satatiih~ `i~ `takowanan~.￺Don't do me wrong / be mean to me.￻不要誤會我
￹`Tatiih~ `ko~ `romi'ad~ `anini~.￺1. This is not an auspicious day.  2. The weather is bad.￻1. 今天是不好預兆的日子  2. 今天天氣不好
